    <div class="tile quadro triple-vertical bg-lighterBlue bg-active-lightBlue" style="padding:10px;">
        At A Thousand Counts we are
        passionate about counting. That's why we are
        creating a video of 1000 counters counting to one thousand.
        You can be one! <br /><br />
        A counter gets assigned a number in the range 1-1000.<br />
