        in sequence so that a video of approximately one hour will be created where
        counters from all over the world are counting to 1000!

        <br /><br />

        Join the movement and count!<br /><br />
        Count passionately. Count lively. Count clearly. Count expectantly.
        But, make sure to count.  <br /><br />
        Be quick and click the pink square. There are only <strong>@ViewBag.CountsLeft</strong> counts left on A Thousand Counts...
